<div class="page-header">
  <h1>Foursquare To Weibo<small> 同步Foursquare签到信息至微博</small></h1>
</div>
<h2><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-globe"></span> 授权管理</h2>
<br>
  <p>
    <% unless @auth.foursquare_token.to_s.empty? %>
    <span><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-thumbs-up"></span> Foursquare 授权已完成</span>
    <% else %>
    <a href="https://foursquare.com/oauth2/authenticate?client_id=
<%= getConf['Foursquare']['client_id'] %>&response_type=
code&redirect_uri=http://foursqtoweibo.herokuapp.com/redirect_uri">
    <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-refresh"></span> Foursquare OAuth2
    </a>
    <% end %>
  </p>
  <p>
    <% unless @auth.weibo_token.to_s.empty? %>
    <span><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-thumbs-up"></span> Weibo 授权已完成</span>
    <% else %>
    <a href="https://api.weibo.com/oauth2/authorize?client_id=
<%= getConf['Weibo']['key'] %>&response_type=code&redirect_uri=
http://foursqtoweibo.herokuapp.com/wei_redirect">
    <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-refresh"></span> Weibo OAuth2
    </a>
    <% end %>
  </p>
  <small><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span> 微博授权有效期仅为90天, 请在过期后重新到当前页面进行授权</small>
